body_text.text:
On HI test, most wild-type BCV samples (39/44) showed very low reactivity (HI titers 1 : 16, Type III) and only three samples showed high reactivity or inhibition (HI titers 1 : 2048–1 : 4096, Type I). One sample was inhibited at 1 : 128, Type II (Fig. 1
). The HI titers of 72 cell culture propagated BCV isolates ranged from 1 : 2–1 : 1024 (Fig. 2
). When a sample was compared after call culture propagation, in most BCV isolates, except WI-17, the HI titers of cell culture propagated BCV were comparatively higher than its wild-type BCV isolate.
